The '''House Malreaux''' were one of the oldest and wealthiest families on the planet of [[Vjun/Legends|Vjun]]. It was founded by the [[First Count Malreaux|First Count]] who was a [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] that extorted his House's noble status from nobles operating around the [[Bay of Tears]] in exchange for a loose promise to not plunder their ships. They lived in a castle named the [[Château Malreaux]]. The family was known for developing the [[Malreaux rose]]. The [[Viscount (title)/Legends|Viscount]] [[Malreaux]] performed experiments on [[Midi-chlorian/Legends|midi-chlorians]] that drove the populace of Vjun insane, leading to them murdering each other in [[29 BBY/Legends|29 BBY]]. One of the few survivors was the Viscountess [[Whirry Malreaux]], who gave her son, [[Whie Malreaux/Legends|Whie]], to the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi Order]] so he could escape the horrors of his birthworld.

